sources.description:
Bolo Yeung, the legendary action villain, plays the heroic master and leader to a cast of real-life martial arts champions.  Shootfighters are part of the Miami fight-to-kill underworld, battling to the death in illegal spectator games of mortal combat run by mobsters and warlords. 

Edited for YouTube standards.

Director: Paul Ziller
1996
Stars: Bolo Yeung, William Zabka (Karate Kid, Cobra Kai), Michael Bernardo
